#: ../../08-build.md:158
msgid ""
"This workflow is intentionally non-blocking. It warns about likely stale PKB "
"docs but does not fail the build just because docs were not updated yet."
msgstr ""
"这个工作流被刻意设计为非阻塞。它会提示哪些 PKB 文档可能已经过期，但不会因为"
"文档尚未更新就直接让构建失败。"

